## SNIPPETS (REFERENCE IMPLEMENTATION HINTS)

**Canonical URL rules (pseudocode):**

```
url = strip_utm(url)
url = force_https(url)
url = remove_trailing_slash(url)
url = remove_tracking_params(url, ["utm_*", "gclid", "fbclid"])
```

**Date coercion:**

```
# parse → aware UTC
published_at = parse_date(src_dt).astimezone(timezone.utc)
keep = (from_utc <= published_at <= to_utc)
```

**Player match score (simplified):**

```
score = 0
if name_in(title): score += 0.7
elif name_in(summary): score += 0.5
if team_overlap(article.teams, player.teams): score += 0.2
emit if score >= 0.7
```

